Version:          0.1.1
Release:          3%{?dist}%{?buildtag}
Summary:          Empirical CDF for Heavy Tailed Data

License:          GPL (>= 3)
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel >= 3.3.0
Requires:         R-core >= 3.3.0
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-rgl 
Requires:         R-CRAN-rgl 

%description
Computes and plots a transformed empirical CDF (ecdf) as a diagnostic for
heavy tailed data, specifically data with power law decay on the tails.
Routines for annotating the plot, comparing data to a model, fitting a
nonparametric model, and some multivariate extensions are given.

